reviewText: The actual episode's are five stars. but since i was expecting so much more, i only give this particular dvd release two stars. There is only a couple episodes of MERMAID MAN AND BARNACLE BOY. WHAT! If you are a TRUE fan of Spongebob and the shows spoofs of the original Batman series [HOLY CRABBY PATTIES, BATMAN], then join me in speaking out. And maybe we can get SHOUT FACTORY's attention or something. Shout Factory is AWESOME about listening to the fans and putting out AWESOME blu-ray (and dvd) releases. And i would like to personally and humbly ask them...... PLEASE GIVE ME A BLU RAY OR DVD RELEASE THAT HAS ALL OF THE EPISODES OF MERMAID MAN AND BARNICLE BOY?? with that said, DON'T BUY this release. Either buy the complete seasons (season three is my favorite) or wait until a better compilation comes out.
Grandson has enjoyed watching this several times!
This was requested from a grandchild as a Christmas gift and that child was thrilled beyond reason.  Entertaining to say the least.

This DVD was good! It wasn't the best SpongeBob DVD made, but it should fit in your collection!!! This DVD includes:

Back to the Past 4/5
The Bad Guy Club For Villains 3.5/5
Keep Bikini Bottom Beautiful 3.5/5
A Pal For Gary 3/5 (I don't like this one, but still watchable)
Yours, Mine and Mine 3.5/5
Kracked Krabs 4.5/5
A Day Without Tears 3.5/5
Summer Job 4.5/5

Includes bonus episode: T.U.F.F Puppy
This movie is great. Bought it as present for an autistic child.  He loves it and still thanks me everytime he sees me.

This is the best separate DVD made for season 7, all the episodes are awesome and really funny if you are looking to buy a spongebob DVD then buy this one because it is the best spongebob DVD made so far. Be sure to add this DVD to you're collection today.
